title: Hour 1 - Patrick Mahomes Is Still Great, Ross Tucker
itunes:title: Hour 1 - Patrick Mahomes Is Still Great, Ross Tucker
description:
Dan was reminded how great Kansas City Chiefs QB Patrick Mahomes really is after they took down the Tom Brady led Tampa Bay Buccaneers last night. And NFL insider Ross Tuck stops by in his regular Monday slot to break down the best and worst of yesterday's NFL action.
